OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,FThe ongoing unrest in the Middle East
OL,8,Fis causing an impact on local farming
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe Ulster Farmers' Union has raised
OL,12,Fconcerns about the supply of
OL,13,Ffertiliser, a significant amount of
OL,14,Fwhich passes through the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz.
OL,17,FUTV spoke to local farmer, John
OL,18,FMcLenaghan on how he is coping with
OL,19,Fthe shortage of fertiliser.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,FFollowing a large delivery of lime to
OL,8,Fmitigate against the shortage, he
OL,9,Facknowledged it's not a proper
OL,10,Falternative to fertiliser.
OL,12,FJohn McLenaghan said: "The lime will
OL,13,Fnot give that fertiliser effect, but
OL,14,Fwhat it will do, it'll help us to
OL,15,Factually balance the soils and then
OL,16,Fhopefully by doing that we'll get a
OL,17,Fbetter use out of the nutrients that
OL,18,Fwe do apply."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,FHe said it's a "real big problem. We
OL,8,Fjust can't get fertiliser. I mean guys
OL,9,Fhad fertiliser ordered and they're not
OL,10,Fgetting the deliveries, they're going
OL,11,Fto try to reorder, they're not getting
OL,12,Fthose reorders."
OL,14,FHe continued: "The merchants don't
OL,15,Fknow themselves when they're getting
OL,16,Fit, the manufacturers don't know if
OL,17,Fthey're going to be able to make it
OL,18,Fbecause they need the raw materials."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,F"So all in all, we're really getting
OL,8,Finto a bad situation at the worst
OL,9,Fpossible time of year.
OL,11,F"Now's the time when our crops are
OL,12,Fwanting to grow and we need to apply
OL,13,Fnutrients at the right time and we
OL,14,Fjust have to try and make the best of
OL,15,Fwhat is available to us and get the
OL,16,Fmost use out of that."
OL,18,FWhat will this mean for consumers?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,FJohn warned of a critical tipping
OL,8,Fpoint for global agriculture, that
OL,9,Fcould be driven by the shortage of
OL,10,Fessential fertilisers.
OL,12,FHe said: "We don't want to be alarmist
OL,13,Fabout it, but we do need this stuff to
OL,14,Fgrow the food that we all consume.
OL,16,F"48% of the world's population
OL,17,Fsurvives because we use these types of
OL,18,Ffertilisers to produce the food that
OL,19,Fthey need. That could be a problem.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,F"At a local level here, farmers will
OL,8,Fuse less because they either feel that
OL,9,Fit's overpriced for them to buy it or
OL,10,Fthey just can't get it.
OL,12,F"Either way, there will be a lower
OL,13,Fsupply, they will grow less product,
OL,14,Fwhatever it happens to be, whether
OL,15,Fit's a cereal crop or a grass crop or
OL,16,Fa vegetable crop, horticulture,
OL,17,Fwhatever it is they'll grow less of it
OL,18,Fif they apply less of the fertiliser.
OL,20,F"That will have a knock-on effect,
OL,21,Fbound to have later on in the year."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
