OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774555873
OL,3,CFarmers face fertiliser shortages as
OL,4,CMiddle East conflict hits food
OL,5,Cproduction
OL,7,FFarmers have said they remain
OL,8,Fcommitted to supplying high-quality
OL,9,Flocal produce.
OL,11,FThe UFU have suggested the current
OL,12,Fsituation reinforces the need for
OL,13,Fstronger domestic production with a
OL,14,Freduction in the reliance of imports.
